Hamlish-Jinja Changelog
========================

Version 0.3.3
--------------

- Allow parenthesis around HTML attributes. (Thanks to https://github.com/rbour)


Version 0.3.2
--------------

- Use the block_start_string, block_end_string, variable_start_string and
  variable_end_string from the jinja environment
  when generating the output. (Thanks to https://github.com/Yajo)


Version 0.3.1
--------------

- Added Python 3.3 support (Thanks to https://github.com/Yajo)


Version 0.3.0
--------------

- Changed license from GPL to BSD (utilities/haml2hamlish.py is still GPL)


Version 0.2.0
-------------

- No changes available

